<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_544" id="271r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_544_r1l2">VVir ~ die <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> etc
                                <expan>Bekenne<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / Daʒ für vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_544_r1l3"><expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> ſind
                                <expan>wılh<ex>elm</ex></expan> Mendell vnd
                            <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Babemberg<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_544_r1l4"><expan>vnſ<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> . Vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns
                                <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> wie Jn der Erber </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_544_r1l5">veſte heinrich Apfaltrer
                            <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        het </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_544_r1l6"><expan>mitname<ex>n</ex></expan> dem
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>vvilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> Mendell j Samat vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_544_r1l7">dem <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Ba<ex>bem</ex>berg<ex>er</ex></expan> iij vardell mit pfeffer die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_544_r1l8">Er Jn <del rend="strikethrough">wider </del>
<expan>gencʒlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wıdergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab . Als vns dẏ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_544_r1l9"><expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> geſagt vnd auch gebeten
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_544_r1l10">daʒ vvir darümb des
                            <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> Aphaltrers freund </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_544_r1l11">werden wolten . vnd alſo werden wir
                                <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_544_r1l12">Aphaltrers ſeiner helffer vnd dyener gut freund </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_544_r1l13">vmb die tat ongeuerde / Mit
                            <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_544" id="271r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir, die <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> etc.,
                            <expan>bekenne<ex>n</ex></expan> etc., daz für uns
                            <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> sind <expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan>
                        Mendell und <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Babemberg<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns
                                <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>, wie in der erber veste Heinrich
                        Apfaltrer <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> het, <expan>mitname<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> Mendell i samat und dem
                                <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Ba<ex>bem</ex>berg<ex>er</ex></expan> iii vardell mit pfeffer, die er
                        in <expan>genczlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab, als uns dy
                            <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> gesagt und auch gebeten
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz wir darümb des
                                <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> Aphaltrers freund werden wolten.
                        Und also werden wir <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Aphaltrers, seiner helffer und dyener gut
                        freund umb die tat ongeverde. Mit <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan> etc. </ab>
</div>
